ultPriceGroupId":"15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","ean":"","gtin":"","asin":"","name_en":"Red Ghost | 2 cm | Pin | Pac-Man","name_pl":"","name_de":"","description_en":"Reclaim a slice of gaming history with this meticulously crafted Pac-Man red ghost enamel pin. Measuring a perfectly compact 2 cm, it's a vibrant tribute to the iconic arcade classic. The design captures the ghost's unmistakable pixelated charm with precise, blocky details: a glossy red body, distinct white eyes featuring deep indigo pupils, and a characteristic jagged mouth. Encased in smooth, durable hard enamel, the pin boasts a polished finish that highlights every nostalgic pixel. A clean black outline defines its retro shape, while the sturdy metal backing ensures secure wear. This small but striking collectible is a must-have for retro game enthusiasts, pin collectors, and anyone who remembers chasing ghosts in the Pac-Man maze. Perfect for pinning on bags, jackets, or adding to your retro gaming display – a tiny time capsule of arcade excitement.","description_pl":"","description_de":"","supplierName":"","supplierLink":"","priceComment":"","stock":0,"price":0,"sizeLength":0,"sizeWidth":0,"weight":0,"length":0,"parameters":[{"parameterId":"0a92f045-7c01-4b06-a0df-ebdf6ab9c24a","value":""},{"parameterId":"8cb8f430-d6c6-4b53-a529-eb3cfaa63d0e","value":""},{"parameterId":"0eadf821-34ff-49bf-8ba7-84f797359f43","value":""},{"parameterId":"ab9d7dc2-632c-4b35-89fc-c6d44752b52e","value":""},{"parameterId":"9c80ceb6-b8ed-47e8-ba07-cbdb602045d5","value":""},{"parameterId":"64a58022-5c7c-46e8-9d07-53c75a94c7dc","value":""}],"imageLinks":["","","","","","","","","","","","","","",""],"createdAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.343Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-28T23:41:55.015Z","images":[{"productId":"7c5c7803-dd3e-4ed7-bbb6-64c28ca29d7e","imageFileId":"d17e4bc1-693d-4de1-bafd-8c281d9e4d36","assignedAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.833Z","imageFile":{"id":"d17e4bc1-693d-4de1-bafd-8c281d9e4d36","filename":"1769643585484-a-3.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA927/1769643585484-a-3.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1717762,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.531Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.531Z"}},{"productId":"7c5c7803-dd3e-4ed7-bbb6-64c28ca29d7e","imageFileId":"2b49adbe-a2d8-42b3-b8ac-4d1666f3f418","assignedAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.833Z","imageFile":{"id":"2b49adbe-a2d8-42b3-b8ac-4d1666f3f418","filename":"1769643585586-a-2.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA927/1769643585586-a-2.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1932718,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.634Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.634Z"}},{"productId":"7c5c7803-dd3e-4ed7-bbb6-64c28ca29d7e","imageFileId":"bf80b409-de01-4765-9b34-4962512b94a9","assignedAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.833Z","imageFile":{"id":"bf80b409-de01-4765-9b34-4962512b94a9","filename":"1769643585689-a-1.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA927/1769643585689-a-1.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":2259483,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.737Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:45.737Z"}}],"catalogs":[{"productId":"7c5c7803-dd3e-4ed7-bbb6-64c28ca29d7e","catalogId":"cad266e9-5a76-4ed3-8e49-a8c7b6bdfc10","assignedAt":"2026-01-28T23:39:46.031Z","catalog":{"id":"cad266e9-5a76-4ed3-8e49-a8c7b6bdfc10","name":"Mentios","description":"","isDefault":true,"defaultLanguageId":"EN","defaultPriceGroupId":"15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","createdAt":"2026-01-19T18:31:41.835Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-20T22:55:07.708Z","languageIds":["cmkhnn6lg0006o3c95op3jhq7","cmkhnn6lg0005o3c9gfxb0ykk","cmkhnn6lg0007o3c92punmjtg","PL","cmkmg9orm0007oac9ni5kehz6","cmkmg9orm0006oac98xheaprk","EN"],"priceGroupIds":["15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","09fa9579-2eb3-4ce8-90b8-576935373e8f"]}}]},{"id":"88ed1eaf-8c49-4c77-83a0-96b4d446a2aa","sku":"KEYCHA925","baseProductId":null,"defaultPriceGroupId":"15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","ean":"","gtin":"","asin":"","name_en":"Dot Devourer | 2 cm | Pin | Pac-Man","name_pl":"Pożeracz Kropki | 2 cm | Przypinka | Pac-Man","name_de":"","description_en":"Step back into the neon-lit streets of Pac-Man with this tiny but iconic collectible pin. Celebrating the game's legendary simplicity, this 2cm enamel pin captures the classic moment where Pac-Man takes a delicious bite out of a glowing dot. Crafted with authentic 8-bit precision, the design features Pac-Man's signature yellow head rendered in bright, glossy hard enamel, perfectly outlined in crisp black to mimic the blocky pixel aesthetics of the original arcade. You'll instantly recognize the character, with its distinctive \"biting\" silhouette showing the dot being devoured – a true piece of gaming history in miniature form. The pin has a satisfyingly solid, slightly raised 3D feel thanks to the enamel filling the metal base, while the back boasts a textured black grid pattern with a standard pin clutch for secure attachment. Wear it on your jacket, hat, or bag and let this pocket-sized slice of retro fun remind you to never lose sight of the dots. Perfect for fans who cherish the magic of Pac-Man!","description_pl":"Wróć na neonowe ulice Pac-Mana dzięki tej małej, ale kultowej przypince kolekcjonerskiej. Świętując legendarne prostotę gry, ta 2-centymetrowa przypinka emaliowa oddaje klasyczny moment, w którym Pac-Man zajada się świecącą kropką. Stworzona z autentyczną precyzją 8-bitową, grafika przedstawia charakterystyczną żółtą głowę Pac-Mana, wykonaną w jasnej, błyszczącej emalii twardej, idealnie obrysowaną wyrazistą czernią, aby naśladować kanciastą, pikselową estetykę oryginalnej gry zręcznościowej. Natychmiast rozpoznasz postać, a jej charakterystyczna sylwetka \"gryząca\" kropkę pokazuje, jak ta znika – prawdziwy kawałek historii gier w miniaturze. Przypinka ma satysfakcjonująco solidny, lekko wypukły trójwymiarowy efekt dzięki emalii wypełniającej metalową podstawę, a tył charakteryzuje się teksturowanym czarnym wzorem siatki oraz standardowym zapięciem motylkowym zapewniającym bezpieczne mocowanie. Noś ją na kurtce, czapce lub torbie i pozwól, aby ten kieszonkowy fragment retro zabawy przypominał Ci, aby nigdy nie tracić z oczu kropek. Idealna dla fanów, którzy cenią magię Pac-Mana!","description_de":"","supplierName":"","supplierLink":"","priceComment":"","stock":4,"price":21,"sizeLength":0,"sizeWidth":0,"weight":0,"length":0,"parameters":[{"parameterId":"0a92f045-7c01-4b06-a0df-ebdf6ab9c24a","value":""},{"parameterId":"8cb8f430-d6c6-4b53-a529-eb3cfaa63d0e","value":""},{"parameterId":"0eadf821-34ff-49bf-8ba7-84f797359f43","value":""},{"parameterId":"ab9d7dc2-632c-4b35-89fc-c6d44752b52e","value":""},{"parameterId":"9c80ceb6-b8ed-47e8-ba07-cbdb602045d5","value":""},{"parameterId":"64a58022-5c7c-46e8-9d07-53c75a94c7dc","value":""}],"imageLinks":["","","","","","","","","","","","","","",""],"createdAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.207Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T22:18:35.020Z","images":[{"productId":"88ed1eaf-8c49-4c77-83a0-96b4d446a2aa","imageFileId":"2101f1a0-28a0-4ad9-81a4-3eccac4c803b","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.709Z","imageFile":{"id":"2101f1a0-28a0-4ad9-81a4-3eccac4c803b","filename":"1769459977354-a-3.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA925/1769459977354-a-3.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1726181,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.405Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.405Z"}},{"productId":"88ed1eaf-8c49-4c77-83a0-96b4d446a2aa","imageFileId":"aa22bdd0-5aa3-4e2d-9df8-87ca7d21f6da","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.709Z","imageFile":{"id":"aa22bdd0-5aa3-4e2d-9df8-87ca7d21f6da","filename":"1769459977470-a-1.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA925/1769459977470-a-1.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1596856,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.516Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.516Z"}},{"productId":"88ed1eaf-8c49-4c77-83a0-96b4d446a2aa","imageFileId":"85e4ff6f-a4d4-46b8-95a7-534227b2f7b8","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.709Z","imageFile":{"id":"85e4ff6f-a4d4-46b8-95a7-534227b2f7b8","filename":"1769459977568-a-2.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA925/1769459977568-a-2.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1642976,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.614Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.614Z"}}],"catalogs":[{"productId":"88ed1eaf-8c49-4c77-83a0-96b4d446a2aa","catalogId":"cad266e9-5a76-4ed3-8e49-a8c7b6bdfc10","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T20:39:37.896Z","catalog":{"id":"cad266e9-5a76-4ed3-8e49-a8c7b6bdfc10","name":"Mentios","description":"","isDefault":true,"defaultLanguageId":"EN","defaultPriceGroupId":"15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","createdAt":"2026-01-19T18:31:41.835Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-20T22:55:07.708Z","languageIds":["cmkhnn6lg0006o3c95op3jhq7","cmkhnn6lg0005o3c9gfxb0ykk","cmkhnn6lg0007o3c92punmjtg","PL","cmkmg9orm0007oac9ni5kehz6","cmkmg9orm0006oac98xheaprk","EN"],"priceGroupIds":["15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","09fa9579-2eb3-4ce8-90b8-576935373e8f"]}}]},{"id":"a1e8f915-ea2c-4161-9dd5-ee54f32c86ac","sku":"KEYCHA924","baseProductId":"","defaultPriceGroupId":"15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","ean":"","gtin":"","asin":"","name_en":"Purple Ghost | 2 cm | Pin | Pac-Man","name_pl":"Fioletowy Duch | 2 cm | Przypinka | Pac-Man","name_de":"","description_en":"Relive the classic arcade adventure with this meticulously crafted Pac-Man ghost pin, perfectly sized at 2cm for subtle style. Designed as Inky, the purple ghost antagonist, this collectible features the iconic pixelated 8-bit sprite art that defined the original game. The pin's bold, vivid purple enamel body captures Inky's signature color, highlighted by sharp white eyes with dark blue pupils and a crisp black outline. Notice the distinctive wavy, serrated bottom edge – a nod to the ghost's 'dripping' motion. Crafted from durable metal with smooth, glossy enamel fill, it offers a raised, 3D finish that shines under light. The black, textured back secures the standard butterfly clasp for easy attachment to jackets, bags, or hats. Each pin is a faithful tribute to the game's retro charm and Inky's unpredictable spirit, making it an essential addition for any Pac-Man fan or retro gaming collector. Wear it proudly and let the ghosts follow!","description_pl":"Przeżyj klasyczną przygodę z automatów dzięki tej starannie wykonanej przypince z duchem z Pac-Mana, o idealnym rozmiarze 2 cm dla subtelnego stylu. Zaprojektowana jako Inky, fioletowy antagonista, ta kolekcjonerska przypinka charakteryzuje się kultową 8-bitową grafiką pikselową, która zdefiniowała oryginalną grę. Odważne, żywe fioletowe szkliwo korpusu oddaje charakterystyczny kolor Inky'ego, podkreślone ostrymi białymi oczami z ciemnoniebieskimi źrenicami i wyraźnym czarnym konturem. Zwróć uwagę na charakterystyczną falistą, ząbkowaną krawędź dolną – nawiązanie do 'kapiącego' ruchu ducha. Wykonana z wytrzymałego metalu z gładkim, błyszczącym wypełnieniem emalią, oferuje podwyższone, trójwymiarowe wykończenie, które błyszczy w świetle. Czarny, teksturowany tył zabezpiecza standardowe zapięcie motylkowe, ułatwiając przymocowanie do kurtek, toreb lub czapek. Każda przypinka to wierne oddanie retro uroku gry i nieprzewidywalnego ducha Inky'ego, co czyni ją niezbędnym dodatkiem dla każdego fana Pac-Mana lub kolekcjonera gier retro. Noś ją z dumą i pozwól duchom podążać za Tobą!","description_de":"","supplierName":"","supplierLink":"","priceComment":"","stock":4,"price":21,"sizeLength":0,"sizeWidth":0,"weight":0,"length":0,"parameters":[{"parameterId":"0a92f045-7c01-4b06-a0df-ebdf6ab9c24a","value":""},{"parameterId":"8cb8f430-d6c6-4b53-a529-eb3cfaa63d0e","value":""},{"parameterId":"0eadf821-34ff-49bf-8ba7-84f797359f43","value":""},{"parameterId":"ab9d7dc2-632c-4b35-89fc-c6d44752b52e","value":""},{"parameterId":"9c80ceb6-b8ed-47e8-ba07-cbdb602045d5","value":""},{"parameterId":"64a58022-5c7c-46e8-9d07-53c75a94c7dc","value":""}],"imageLinks":["","","","","","","","","","","","","","",""],"createdAt":"2026-01-26T11:41:34.707Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T20:38:20.826Z","images":[{"productId":"a1e8f915-ea2c-4161-9dd5-ee54f32c86ac","imageFileId":"0d571c68-2a68-4b5d-9751-9496454177a6","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T20:38:20.556Z","imageFile":{"id":"0d571c68-2a68-4b5d-9751-9496454177a6","filename":"1769427694890-a-3.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA000/1769427694890-a-3.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1834619,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-26T11:41:34.942Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T11:41:34.942Z"}},{"productId":"a1e8f915-ea2c-4161-9dd5-ee54f32c86ac","imageFileId":"38c6d7c8-6415-476c-bed6-bfcbafd850dd","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T20:38:20.556Z","imageFile":{"id":"38c6d7c8-6415-476c-bed6-bfcbafd850dd","filename":"1769427694998-a-1.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA000/1769427694998-a-1.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1848240,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-26T11:41:35.054Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T11:41:35.054Z"}},{"productId":"a1e8f915-ea2c-4161-9dd5-ee54f32c86ac","imageFileId":"cc8d8ba7-edc7-450e-a24f-dfc20ddcb300","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T20:38:20.556Z","imageFile":{"id":"cc8d8ba7-edc7-450e-a24f-dfc20ddcb300","filename":"1769427695135-a-2.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA000/1769427695135-a-2.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1740904,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-26T11:41:35.189Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T11:41:35.189Z"}}],"catalogs":[{"productId":"a1e8f915-ea2c-4161-9dd5-ee54f32c86ac","catalogId":"cad266e9-5a76-4ed3-8e49-a8c7b6bdfc10","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T20:38:20.826Z","catalog":{"id":"cad266e9-5a76-4ed3-8e49-a8c7b6bdfc10","name":"Mentios","description":"","isDefault":true,"defaultLanguageId":"EN","defaultPriceGroupId":"15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","createdAt":"2026-01-19T18:31:41.835Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-20T22:55:07.708Z","languageIds":["cmkhnn6lg0006o3c95op3jhq7","cmkhnn6lg0005o3c9gfxb0ykk","cmkhnn6lg0007o3c92punmjtg","PL","cmkmg9orm0007oac9ni5kehz6","cmkmg9orm0006oac98xheaprk","EN"],"priceGroupIds":["15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","09fa9579-2eb3-4ce8-90b8-576935373e8f"]}}]},{"id":"78e96b54-4240-4717-b102-42b4eafa1b4a","sku":"KEYCHA923","baseProductId":null,"defaultPriceGroupId":"15ba906f-e2d1-4a0e-995f-67047a011ae5","ean":"","gtin":"","asin":"","name_en":"Ryu | 4 cm | Pin | Street Fighter","name_pl":"Ryu | 4 cm | Przypinka | Street Fighter","name_de":"","description_en":"Step into the arena with this meticulously crafted *Street Fighter II* enamel pin set. Perfectly capturing the iconic 8-bit aesthetic of the original game, the set features two distinct 4 cm pins. One pin depicts Ryu himself in a dynamic, leaping fighting stance, showcasing his classic red headband and gloves, orange gi, blue trousers, and white skin tone in crisp pixel art. The second pin brings his signature Hadoken attack to life—a circular burst of blue energy rendered with precise pixel detailing, using various shades to create the illusion of depth and power. Both pins are crafted from high-quality metal with smooth, glossy hard enamel fills, featuring a clean silver metal border that defines their retro shapes. The rear of each pin has a subtle textured pattern for secure attachment. Adorn your jacket, bag, or hat with this nostalgic tribute to Ryu's martial arts journey and the timeless energy of the *Street Fighter II* legacy.","description_pl":"Wejdź na arenę z tym starannie wykonanym zestawem przypinek emaliowanych z gry *Street Fighter II*. Doskonale oddającym kultową estetykę 8-bitową oryginalnej gry, zestaw zawiera dwie odrębne przypinki o wymiarach 4 cm. Jedna z nich przedstawia samego Ryu w dynamicznej, skaczącej pozycji walki, ukazując jego klasyczną czerwoną opaskę i rękawice, pomarańczowy gi, niebieskie spodnie i jasną karnację skóry w wyraźnej pikselowej grafice. Druga przypinka ożywia jego charakterystyczny atak Hadoken – okrągłą eksplozję niebieskiej energii, oddaną z precyzyjnymi pikselowymi detalami, wykorzystując różne odcienie, aby stworzyć iluzję głębi i mocy. Obie przypinki wykonane są z wysokiej jakości metalu z gładkimi, błyszczącymi wypełnieniami z twardej emalii, z czystą srebrną metalową obwódką, która podkreśla ich retro kształty. Tył każdej przypinki posiada subtelny, teksturowany wzór zapewniający bezpieczne mocowanie. Udekoruj swoją kurtkę, torbę lub czapkę tym nostalgicznym ukłonem w stronę podróży Ryu w sztukach walki i ponadczasowej energii dziedzictwa *Street Fighter II*.","description_de":"","supplierName":"","supplierLink":"","priceComment":"","stock":4,"price":40,"sizeLength":0,"sizeWidth":0,"weight":0,"length":0,"parameters":[{"parameterId":"0a92f045-7c01-4b06-a0df-ebdf6ab9c24a","value":""},{"parameterId":"8cb8f430-d6c6-4b53-a529-eb3cfaa63d0e","value":""},{"parameterId":"0eadf821-34ff-49bf-8ba7-84f797359f43","value":""},{"parameterId":"ab9d7dc2-632c-4b35-89fc-c6d44752b52e","value":""},{"parameterId":"9c80ceb6-b8ed-47e8-ba07-cbdb602045d5","value":""},{"parameterId":"64a58022-5c7c-46e8-9d07-53c75a94c7dc","value":""}],"imageLinks":["","","","","","","","","","","","","","",""],"createdAt":"2026-01-26T10:41:30.788Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T11:51:36.492Z","images":[{"productId":"78e96b54-4240-4717-b102-42b4eafa1b4a","imageFileId":"f7800ba7-454e-4ab2-90d3-8d4c17366453","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T10:41:31.324Z","imageFile":{"id":"f7800ba7-454e-4ab2-90d3-8d4c17366453","filename":"1769424090939-a-2.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA923/1769424090939-a-2.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1479486,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-26T10:41:30.987Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-26T10:41:30.987Z"}},{"productId":"78e96b54-4240-4717-b102-42b4eafa1b4a","imageFileId":"078b1fbe-75ae-47c7-872a-83d1b9d3ec0a","assignedAt":"2026-01-26T10:41:31.324Z","imageFile":{"id":"078b1fbe-75ae-47c7-872a-83d1b9d3ec0a","filename":"1769424091075-a-1.png","filepath":"/uploads/products/KEYCHA923/1769424091075-a-1.png","mimetype":"image/png","size":1179891,"width":null,"height":null,"createdAt":"2026-01-26T10:41:31.126Z","updatedAt":"2026-01